    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "### Description\n\nIt would be neat to have an LspToggle command that would detect if any configs were already started and do LspStop in that case or otherwise do LspStart.\n\nThen such command could be assigned to some key for easy access instead of having one key for starting and another key for stopping.\n\nIs there some way to implement such functionality using current lspconfig API? I could at least make a custom command myself if it's doable.",
