        {
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "After digging around, this works well enough if anyone needs (assigning toggle to F10):\n\n```lua\n-- toggle LSP for the current buffer\nvim.keymap.set('n', '<F10>', function()\n  -- clients active for the current buffer\n  local clients = vim.lsp.get_clients({ bufnr = vim.api.nvim_get_current_buf() })\n\n  if vim.tbl_isempty(clients) then\n    vim.cmd(\"LspStart\")\n  else\n    vim.cmd(\"LspStop\")\n  end\nend)\n```\n",
            "created_at": "2025-03-30T19:28:20Z",
            "html_url": "https://github.com/neovim/nvim-lspconfig/issues/3678#issuecomment-2764709716",
